            <title type="text">Install Hugo in Windows</title>
            <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://starspiritstorm.github.io/en/posts/install-hugo-in-windows/" />
            <id>https://starspiritstorm.github.io/en/posts/install-hugo-in-windows/</id>
            <updated>2022-03-15T08:00:00&#43;08:00</updated>
            <published>2022-03-15T08:00:00&#43;08:00</published>
            <author>
                    <name>starspiritstorm</name>
                    <uri>https://starspiritstorm.github.io/en/</uri>
                    <email>starspiritstorm@gmail.com</email>
                    </author>
            <rights>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.en)</rights><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Installing hugo.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
            
                <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Installing hugo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;install-hugo&#34;&gt;Install Hugo&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After finished installing chocolatey, just simply open up powershell, and type&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;choco install hugo -confirm
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://starspiritstorm.github.io/images/install_hugo/fig1.Install_hugo.png&#34; alt=&#34;fig1&#34; title=&#34;Fig1. Install hugo&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then install hugo extended, type&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;choco install hugo-extended -confirm
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://starspiritstorm.github.io/images/install_hugo/fig2.Install_hugo_extended.png&#34; alt=&#34;fig2&#34; title=&#34;Fig2. Install hugo extended&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And done.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;check-hugo-version-and-uninstall-hugo&#34;&gt;Check Hugo version and Uninstall Hugo&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Two simple command.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check version&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;hugo version
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Uninstall hugo&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;choco uninstall hugo
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://starspiritstorm.github.io/images/install_hugo/fig3.Check_hugo_version&amp;amp;Uninstall_hugo.png&#34; alt=&#34;fig3&#34; title=&#34;Fig3. Check_hugo_version&amp;amp;Uninstall_hugo&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
            
            
            
            
            
                
                    
                        
                            
                            
                            
