        <entry>
            <title type="text">Install Chocolatey in Windows</title>
            <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://starspiritstorm.github.io/en/posts/install-chocolatey-in-windows/" />
            <id>https://starspiritstorm.github.io/en/posts/install-chocolatey-in-windows/</id>
            <updated>2021-12-21T14:53:55&#43;08:00</updated>
            <published>2021-12-21T14:53:55&#43;08:00</published>
            <author>
                    <name>starspiritstorm</name>
                    <uri>https://starspiritstorm.github.io/en/</uri>
                    <email>starspiritstorm@gmail.com</email>
                    </author>
            <rights>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.en)</rights><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;For the purpose of installing hugo, we need to install package manager - Chocolatey for Windows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This article will introduce how to install Chocolatey in Windows environment.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
            
                <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;For the purpose of installing hugo, we need to install package manager - Chocolatey for Windows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This article will introduce how to install Chocolatey in Windows environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;install-chocolatey&#34;&gt;Install Chocolatey&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First, go to the official web site of Chocolatey&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://chocolatey.org/&#34;&gt;Chocolatey official site&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://chocolatey.org/install&#34;&gt;Chocolatey official site of install instruction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://starspiritstorm.github.io/images/install_chocolately/fig1.Instruction_of_install_chocolately.png&#34; alt=&#34;fig1&#34; title=&#34;Fig1. Official web site of Chocolatey install instruction&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;install-step-1-using-system-administrator-to-open-windows-power-shell&#34;&gt;Install step 1. Using System Administrator to open Windows Power Shell&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The command needs Windows Power Shell to execute, remember using System Administrator to open Windows Power Shell&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;![fig2](/images/install_chocolately/fig2.start_power_shell_with_admin.png &amp;ldquo;Fig2. Right click icon and select &amp;ldquo;Run as administrator&amp;rdquo; Windows Power Shell&amp;rdquo;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;install-step-2-execute-the-command-from-chocolatey-install-instruction&#34;&gt;Install step 2. Execute the command from Chocolatey install instruction&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to Chocolatey install instruction, if you have some authority control issue, you better go to the MSDN to check which authority level you required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To check the setting of your Power Shell, you can using the following command.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Get-ExecutionPolicy -list
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://starspiritstorm.github.io/images/install_chocolately/fig3.check_ExecutionPolicy.png&#34; alt=&#34;fig3&#34; title=&#34;Fig3. Check your ExecutionPolicy&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then you can run the &amp;ldquo;run following command&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://starspiritstorm.github.io/images/install_chocolately/fig4.run_following_command.png&#34; alt=&#34;fig4&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol -bor 3072; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString(&#39;https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1&#39;))
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that command has written the &amp;ldquo;Bypass&amp;rdquo;, so your Set-ExecutionPolicy will be set to Bypass, -Scope Process means only applied for Process&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using &amp;ldquo;AllSigned&amp;rdquo; will get multiple queries, it depends on your needs to decide using Bypass or AllSigned, I&amp;rsquo;m just lazy person so I just using Bypass.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://starspiritstorm.github.io/images/install_chocolately/fig5.Bypass.png&#34; alt=&#34;fig5&#34; title=&#34;Fig5. Bypass&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://starspiritstorm.github.io/images/install_chocolately/fig6.AllSigned.png&#34; alt=&#34;fig6&#34; title=&#34;Fig6. AllSigned&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After finished, you will see Chocolatey (choco.exe) is now ready.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://starspiritstorm.github.io/images/install_chocolately/fig7.Chocolately_ready.png&#34; alt=&#34;fig7&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
            
            
            
            
            
                
                    
                        
                            
                            
                            
